## Executive Summary

Saudi B2B companies in {{ sector }} consistently face the same structural gap: accounts sit in spreadsheets, priorities shift daily without an objective standard, and sales teams spend their time preparing lists rather than having conversations. This proposal scopes the **Revenue Intelligence Sprint** — a fixed-price (499 SAR), fixed-duration (seven days) engagement that converts your existing data into a ranked account list with explainable evidence and bilingual draft communications, ready for your review — not for automatic sending.

Every step in this sprint is governed. Every decision is logged before any external action is taken. Nothing is sent on your behalf without your explicit, recorded approval.

